{"tid":1640011,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「建議」一陣睇天琦既手足","createTime":"2019-10-08T22:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T23:57:47.000Z","uid":232082,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ed231c0ab5548dd44d7c52caf745777a7460fa4e","tid":1640011,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:23:28.000Z","msg":"各位好<br />\n一陣剩係會派129張飛<br />\n我知道大家都好想見天琦一面<br />\n不過仲有 盧建民義士 同 黃家駒義士 既家人<br />\n佢地都好想見到自己屋企人一面<br />\n我知道庭內有家屬位 不過未必足夠<br />\n希望一陣有飛既人足可以考慮睇完天琦再出去傳張飛比其他人<br />\n尤其係義士既家人<br />\n審訊結果大家都會知<br />\n到場既都係想支持香港黑暗中既一點明光"},{"pid":"ebddb942396240645a78edaa228231cabf858400","tid":1640011,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:23:54.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"4c1b84ffd9e0c129d66caba4277053c12c5db006","tid":1640011,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:24:08.000Z","msg":"請推"},{"pid":"523bcfb0eca797ca742528b875afc372819aff28","tid":1640011,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:24:18.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"a8666f8bb6d64a503b37b3c17e64716eef107a10","tid":1640011,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:24:29.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"1c990e07b432b62c7bd32a41dd264d964a59b09d","tid":1640011,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:24:41.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"80ebbacbfb86657067a43b96ada86e51298852dc","tid":1640011,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:24:52.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"425128ce5a0ae2a854cc65b985bd21704bbe9917","tid":1640011,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:25:04.000Z","msg":"推5/10"},{"pid":"88103ea75352ba941e8f33fe15b4e178b583c62c","tid":1640011,"uid":232082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T22:25:15.000Z","msg":"推6/10"},{"pid":"f22293b5